                <li><strong>No IP logging</strong> or fingerprinting.</li>
            </ul>

            <br />

            <h2>Your Privacy Choices</h2>
            <p>Since we do not collect personal data, there are no forms, accounts, or opt-out requirements.</p>
            <p>If you wish to delete the light/dark mode cookie, you can do so via your browser settings.</p>

            <br />

            <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p>If we make changes to how this website handles privacy, this page will be updated accordingly.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact me at <a href="webmaster@devenney.io">webmaster@devenney.io</a>.</p>
